headline: HWM Q2 Deep Dive: Aerospace Growth Outpaces Headwinds, Market Reacts to Outlook Uncertainty
summary: Aerospace and defense company Howmet (NYSE:HWM) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 9.2% year on year to $2.05 billion. The company expects next quarter’s revenue to be around $2.03 billion, close to analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.91 per share was 4.2% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
